Joshua C. Martin

Bio

Applied microeconomist with interests in Labor, Household and Urban Economics.

Postdoctoral Researcher at Vanderbilt University. Housed in the Department of Economics, Center for Research on Inequality & Health and the LGBTQ+ Policy Lab.

Email: joshua.martin@vanderbilt.edu

Employment

  • Vanderbilt University (Postdoc; 2023-)

  • Berry College (VAP while ABD; 2022-2023)

Education

  • West Virginia University (2018-2023)
    • PhD: Economics
  • Oklahoma State University (2013-2017)
    • BS: Economics; Minor: Math, French
